text: Lapinjärvi () is a municipality in Uusimaa, Finland. As of 30 September 2023, 2,465 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Iitti, Kouvola, Loviisa, Myrskylä and Orimattila. The lake Lapinjärvi is in the municipality. The municipality speaks both Finnish and Swedish. == Other websites == * Municipality of Lapinjärvi – Official website Category:Municipalities of Uusimaa
